title: Uncanny X-Force 009 (2013) (Digital) (G85-Empire)
description: The Fantomex Love Pentagram explodes!With the truth about their sordid past fully revealed, can Fantomex, Psylocke, and Cluster look each other in the eye?Every psychic ninja needs a vicious animal with no impulse control and a short temper to back her up...right?Puck! Man, does that guy love jerky. Especially buffalo and bison jerky, dipped in Canadian whiskey.Plus: a terrifying surprise villain from the X-past is definitely playing chess, not checkers, across Los Angeles.
